events.info: Running Times Doors: 6:00pm Start: TBA *Please note all times are approximate & subject to change. Australia, we hope you are ready for the metalcore tour of the year. events.info: Doors 6:00pm Pub Choir is FINALLY coming back to Brisbane this September 27th at Fortitude Music Hall. Triumphant (we're manifesting success), and likely armed with some wild stories from the road, we'll be absolutely frothing to make happy music with our original and best audience (that's you, Brisbane). It's time to get your choir squad back together for a night of laughing, singing, and big smiling.
